{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/animal-feed-registration-tool.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/animal-feed-registration-tool","title":"Animal feed registration","format":"transaction","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:10:58+00:00","details":{"need_id":"B946","business_proposition":true,"description":"Record your animal feed activities with your local council and Veterinary Medicines Directorate's Animal Medicines Inspectorate","language":"en","alternative_title":"Record your animal feed activities","more_information":"<p>This tool uses <a href=\"/government-gateway\" title=\"Government Gateway\">Government Gateway</a>. </p>\n\n<h2>Getting help</h2>\n<p>Contact the <abbr title=\"Department for Environmental Food and Rural Affairs\">Defra</abbr> Helpline if you have any queries about animal feed registration.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Department for Environmental Food and Rural Affairs\">Defra</abbr> Helpline</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#111;&#110;&#108;&#105;&#110;&#101;&#104;&#101;&#108;&#112;&#064;&#100;&#101;&#102;&#114;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#111;&#110;&#108;&#105;&#110;&#101;&#104;&#101;&#108;&#112;&#064;&#100;&#101;&#102;&#114;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a> <br />\n08459 33 55 77 <br />\nMonday to Friday, 9am to 5pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Agents</h2>\n<p>Sign up as an <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://secure.services.defra.gov.uk/wps/portal/wfa/!ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gzdx8LQyd_A0t3X3dHA08fM1fvAEdXY3cTI6B8JE55A3dDSnQbmBHQHQ5yLX7b8cmDzAfJG-AAjgb6fh75uan6BbmhEQaZAekAekimGQ!!/dl3/d3/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/\" title=\"Sign up as an agent for Defra farm surveys and assessments\">agent</a> if you want to use the animal feed registration tool for more than one farmer.</p>\n\n<h2>Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"/find-your-local-council\" title=\"Find your local council\">Contact your local council</a> to apply for animal feed registration in Scotland or Wales, or the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.dardni.gov.uk/index/fisheries-farming-and-food/supply-industries/animal-feeds.htm\" title=\"DARD - animal feeds\">Department of Agriculture and Rural Development</a> (<abbr title=\"Department of Agriculture and Rural Development\">DARD</abbr>) in Northern Ireland.</p>\n\n","introduction":"<p>Animal Feed Registration is part of <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://rpa.defra.gov.uk/rpa/index.nsf/UIMenu/814240C66F10CAC8802570C7004248D4?Opendocument\" title=\"Cross compliance (Rural Payments Agency)\">cross compliance.</a> You must register animal feed with your local council to get your farming subsidy under the <a href=\"/single-payment-scheme-online\" title=\"Manage your Single Payment Scheme online\">Single Payment Scheme</a>. Completing the registration online is quicker, easier and lets you make changes if your circumstances change.</p>\n","will_continue_on":"Defra farm surveys and assessments","link":"https://secure.services.defra.gov.uk/wps/portal/wfa/!ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gzdx8LQyd_A0t3X3dHA08fM1fvAEdXYwNTI6B8JG55AzMCusNB9uFW4W6OXx5kPkjeAAdwNND388jPTdUvyI0wyAxIVwQAzhGtrA!!/dl3/d3/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/","alternate_methods":"\n","minutes_to_complete":"","expectations":["Available in England only"]},"tags":[{"title":"Farming","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business%2Ffarming.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Health and safety, registering and licensing animals, compliance tools","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business%2Ffarming","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/farming"},"parent":{"title":"Businesses and self-employed","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Information about starting up and running a business in the UK, including hel